Installation Instructions
--------------------------

1) Clone stephenhardy/dotfiles.git into ~/bin/dotfiles

  > cd ~/bin
  > git clone git@github.com:stephenhardy/dotfiles.git dotfiles

2) Point ~/.bashrc to our dotfiles/bashrc file

  > echo '. ~/bin/dotfiles/bashrc' >> ~/.bashrc

3) Run the updated .bashrc file

  > . ~/.bashrc

  *** In future you can use the reload (created in dotfiles/bash/aliases) command to source all the dotfiles ***
